<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">سورة الشعراء الآية:</span> ٩٧.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>سورة النحل،<span class="c5"> من الآية:</span> ٣٨.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
